<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فَهُمَا عَلَى كُلِّ امْرِءٍ فَرْضَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَالْهِجْرَةُ الأُولَى إِلى الرَّحْمَنِ بِالـ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِخْلاصِ فِي سِرٍّ وَفي إِعْلانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَالْقَصْدُ وَجْهُ اللهِ بِالأَقْوَالِ وَالـ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَعْمَالِ وَالطَّاعَاتِ وَالشُّكرَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَبِذَاكَ يَنْجُو الْعَبْدُ مِنْ إِشْرَاكِهِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَيَصِيرُ حَقًّا عَابِدَ الرَّحْمَنِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَالْهِجْرةُ الأُخْرَى إِلى الْمَبْعُوثِ بِالْـ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>حَقِّ الْمُبِينِ وَوَاضِحِ الْبُرْهَانِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَيَدُورُ مَعْ قَوْلِ الرَّسُولِ وَفِعْلِهِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>نَفِيًا وَإِثْبَاتًا بِلاَ رَوَغَانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وُيُحَكِّمُ الْوَحْيَ الْمُبينَ عَلَى الذِي<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>قَالَ الشُّيوخُ فَعِنْدَهُ حَكَمَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>لاَ يَحْكُُمَانِ بِبَاطِلٍ أبَدًا وَكُلُّ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>الْعَدْلِ قَدْ جَاءَتْ بِهِ الْحَكَمَانِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَهُمَا كِتَابُ اللهِ أَعْدَلَ حَاكِمٍ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فِيهِ الشِّفَا وَهِدَايَةُ الْحَيْرَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَالْحَاكِمُ الثَّاني كَلامُ رَسُولِهِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مَا ثَمَّ غَيْرُهُمَا لِذِي إِيمَانِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَإِذَا دَعَوْكَ لِغَيْرِ حُكْمِهِمَا فَلا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>سَمْعًا لِدَاعِي الْكُفْرِ وَالْعِصْيَانِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>